{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-simple-markdown-js","path":"/developer-portal/typography/","matchPath":"","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#typography\" aria-label=\"typography permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><div class=\"hidden-anchor\" id=\"typography\"></div>Typography</h1>\n<h2 style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#change-the-font\" aria-label=\"change the font permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><div class=\"hidden-anchor\" id=\"change-the-font\"></div>Change the font</h2>\n<p>Import your font(s).\nFonts are imported in the <code class=\"language-text\">siteConfig.yaml</code> file.</p>\n<div class=\"code-wrapper\">\n        <div class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n             data-toaster-id=\"45704168007106440000\"\n             data-toaster-duration=\"1500\"\n             onClick=\"copyCodeToClipboard(`stylesheets:\n  - https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:300,400,600,700`, `45704168007106440000`)\"\n        >\n          <div class=\"gatsby-code-button\" title=\"Copy the code snippet\">Copy</div>\n          <div class=\"done-indicator done-indicator-45704168007106440000\">Copied</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">stylesheets</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> https<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>//fonts.googleapis.com/css<span class=\"token punctuation\">?</span>family=Roboto<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">300</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">400</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">600</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">700</span></code></pre></div>\n      </div>\n<p>We'll add another font.</p>\n<div class=\"code-wrapper\">\n        <div class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n             data-toaster-id=\"31494997047785423000\"\n             data-toaster-duration=\"1500\"\n             onClick=\"copyCodeToClipboard(`stylesheets:\n  - https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:300,400,600,700\n  - https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Source+Sans+Pro:300,400,600,700&display=swap`, `31494997047785423000`)\"\n        >\n          <div class=\"gatsby-code-button\" title=\"Copy the code snippet\">Copy</div>\n          <div class=\"done-indicator done-indicator-31494997047785423000\">Copied</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">stylesheets</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> https<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>//fonts.googleapis.com/css<span class=\"token punctuation\">?</span>family=Roboto<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">300</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">400</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">600</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">700</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> https<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>//fonts.googleapis.com/css<span class=\"token punctuation\">?</span>family=Source+Sans+Pro<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">300</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">400</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">600</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>700<span class=\"token important\">&amp;display=swap</span></code></pre></div>\n      </div>\n<p>Add fonts from any sources (as long as you have the license to do so).</p>\n<p>Adjust the fonts in the typography sections of <code class=\"language-text\">theme.ts</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-wrapper\">\n        <div class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n             data-toaster-id=\"23569363756042130000\"\n             data-toaster-duration=\"1500\"\n             onClick=\"copyCodeToClipboard(`  typography: {\n    fontSize: '16px',\n    lineHeight: '1.5em',\n    fontWeightRegular: '400',\n    fontWeightBold: '600',\n    fontWeightLight: '300',\n    fontFamily: '&quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif',\n    headings: {\n      fontFamily: '&quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif',\n      fontWeight: '600',\n    },`, `23569363756042130000`)\"\n        >\n          <div class=\"gatsby-code-button\" title=\"Copy the code snippet\">Copy</div>\n          <div class=\"done-indicator done-indicator-23569363756042130000\">Copied</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ts\"><pre class=\"language-ts\"><code class=\"language-ts\">  typography<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    fontSize<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'16px'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    lineHeight<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'1.5em'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    fontWeightRegular<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'400'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    fontWeightBold<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'600'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    fontWeightLight<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'300'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    fontFamily<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'\"Source Sans Pro\", sans-serif'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    headings<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      fontFamily<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'\"Source Sans Pro\", sans-serif'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      fontWeight<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'600'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre></div>\n      </div>\n<p>Notice that \"Source Sans Pro\" is in quotes because of the spaces in the name.</p>\n<p>Also, adjust the <code class=\"language-text\">fontSize</code> and experiment to find your style.</p>","headings":[{"value":"Typography","depth":1},{"value":"Change the font","depth":2}]},"contentItem":{"data":{"lastModified":"2022-07-05T12:23:21.000Z","enableToc":null,"disableLastModified":null,"tocMaxDepth":null,"requestLogin":false}},"siteConfig":{"enableToc":false,"disableLastModified":false,"tocMaxDepth":4}},"pag